  </li>
  <li>
    <p>When the gentlemen rose to go away, Mrs. Bennet was <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="mindful of"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(考虑到某事/记着/想着)</code></b> her intended civility, and they were invited and engaged to dine at Longbourn in a few day’s time.</p>
